{
  "stem": "23428.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was an interesting scene, because my brother and I, being very religious still at that time, spent a lot of time on our knees praying.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody else around was swinging and singing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And also, in order to get fresh air, just a little bit of fresh air, Max and I volunteered, I think daily, to-- to clean the halls with wet-- with wet-- with wet rags, so they let us out of the cell for cleaning purposes.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] in ways which I don't remember now, we must have encountered somebody during the cleaning work who had seen my father.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We knew that he was also there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in fact, he sent a message to us whether we could get him some cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was a chain smoker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he wanted to swap a few slices of bread and get cigarettes from somebody, which of course we couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Now, we also knew that my mother was there, obviously, because she was taken in, some other part of the prison, together with my brother.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that was it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, it was overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was obviously not very good food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I suspect it was, again, a bowl of soup a day, maybe a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you see, you understand from my background, since we were free-- living freely until late July '44 without any economic restrictions, we were very sporty and-- and well-fed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think undernourishment didn't hit us as much as people who had-- didn't have such a fortunate background.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
